<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Bloccit</h1>
  <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
  <p>
      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> or 
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> today!
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Learn Something New!</h2>
    <p>Ever wonder why everyone is full of fun facts and you're not? Why all your friends know the jokes you tell them? Get with the program - join Bloccit!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Share Your Knowledge</h2>
    <p>We are giving you this big beautiful soapbox, so don't waste it by spewing filth - we do want to know about that one time your grandma asked what a "twerk" is. That is golden.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Join the Conversation</h2>
    <p>Get connected with local, national, and international populations to see how small the world truly is. We're here for all kinds, we welcome you to share your opinion.</p>
  </div>
</div>